channel.title: [DELTA] Login button not showing [/DELTA]

k, I followed this tutorial http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/60272-adding-custom-login-boxs-buttons.html and everything went good with the custom login! BUT, Only 1 of the login Buttons shows up, the others are still the default buttons.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/mOM1oyT.png[/img]
The one on the left is correct! but on the right is wrong. Any help is well appreciated! If you have any ideas please let me know! Thank you!
